labyrinth.pathfinding

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • labyrinth.builder.Place
      • labyrinth.pathfinding.Node

  • public class Node
extends Place
    This class save the node information. Save the parent node, calculates the values of the node and allow other classes to know them. The end variable allow the class to calculate the heuristic value.
    Author:
    Daniel Castaño Estrella
